--- !u!114 &1235419534
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1235419532}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<size=24>The Basics<size=14>\n\nIn <b>Scoundrel Plus</b>, your goal is
    to defeat each 4-card room in the dungeon until you \nfind a <b>Door Card</b>
    to progress to the next level.\n\nWhenever you enter a room you are presented
    with four cards:\n\r\n- <color=#930000><b>DIAMONDS</b></color> are <u>weapons</u>
    - their power is equal to their value. \r\n\t- If you equip a weapon it replaces
    your current one\n\r\n- <color=#930000><b>HEARTS</b></color> are <u>potions</u>
    - they heal you equal to your value\r\n\t- Only your FIRST potion per room will
    count; any others rest will be discarded if used.\n\r\n- <color=#405A8C><b>CLUBS</b></color>
    and <color=#405A8C><b>SPADES</b></color> are <u>monsters</u> - you may attack
    them with your <u>weapon</u> (if you have one) or your <u>fists</u>:\n\r\n\t-
    <u>Weapon:</u> You take damage equal to the difference of the monster's value
    vs your weapon's and defeat it\r\n\t\t  Your weapon can only attack a monster
    with a value LOWER than the previously slain monster\n\r\n\t- <u>Fists:</u> You
    take damage equal to the monster's value and defeat it\r\n\r\nYou may use cards
    in any order.\n\nDefeating monsters grants you 1 gold, <u>clearing the entire
    room</u> grants you 2 extra gold. Spend gold on upgrades.\r\n\r\nIf your health
    reaches 0, you <u><b>die</b></u>.\n\nCards get more powers as the game goes on.
    Hover over a card with an icon to see the power.\r\r\n\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 75264fa9e13da2b41919fefa895e40a6, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 255578546575997133, guid: 75264fa9e13da2b41919fefa895e40a6, type: 2}
